{"tid":1276094,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"建議打去電台表達意見","createTime":"2019-07-02T01:24:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T00:36:13.000Z","uid":30791,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"367287d78d9f44c05e1123411c0ca0e8dc69ac9a","tid":1276094,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T01:24:04.000Z","msg":"可考慮以下幾點<br />\n1. 重申 不能沒有獨立調查委員會 強調監警會無用 自己人查自己人 警察身有屎 怕獨立調查<br />\n2. 警察濫權比一般市民犯法嚴重 警察係公僕 知法犯法 罪加一等 而政府打算包庇<br />\n3. 警察徇私枉法 放過支持警察打人的示威者 卻檢控遇襲的反對者<br />\n4. 表示試過和平示威沒有用<br />\n5. 其它 請討論"},{"pid":"00887b8b20f122352f580f341a2b8ab09492f5e2","tid":1276094,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T01:34:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99b352d151994b386d3fc301076bff534f5d78bc","tid":1276094,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T01:37:01.000Z","msg":"6. 回應佐級協會 並非政治問題 是警察濫權犯法問題"},{"pid":"e7f0656ec4a2fbf1a2b4ff3e1f54d3e74f694303","tid":1276094,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T02:21:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ee654e202b71c2b6bb02dd6e2d76eac2bdac8fa","tid":1276094,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T03:31:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3b114a9d8c73b35d2c54328e210cd36f3b2ae93","tid":1276094,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:17:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce49e73b582ad3b8426242320a37d9210002c956","tid":1276094,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:12:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5423fd346e5aab2a4c67fca1e1f96440d3dd73e9","tid":1276094,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB